          "type": "math",
          "latex": "7.5 \\text{ N/mm}^2 = \\frac{150 \\times 400 \\text{ N}}{\\frac{1}{6} \\times \\frac{\\pi}{4} D^2}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Area of bolts = $\\pi D^2 / 4$"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Area of 8 bolts = $\\pi D^2 / 4$"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "1 bolt = $1/6 \\times \\pi D^2 / 4$"
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "D^2 = \\frac{150 \\times 400 \\times 4 \\times 6}{3.14 \\times 7.5}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "D^2 = \\frac{2 \\times 4 \\times 6 \\times 400}{3.14} = \\frac{19200}{3.14} = 6114.649",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "D = \\sqrt{\\frac{19200}{3.14}} = 78.196 \\text{ MM}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Quest: The diameter of a piston in Steam engine is 300 mm and maximum pressure acting is $0.7 N/mm^2$, maximum compression strength is $40 N/mm^2$. Find the diameter of connecting rod?"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Solution: Given:"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "D=piston diameter = 300 mm"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "stress in piston $\\sigma_p = 0.7 N/mm^2$"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Stress on connecting rod $\\sigma_R = 40 N/mm^2$"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "$d = \\text{diameter of connecting rod} = ?$"
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\sigma_P = \\frac{P_{load}}{\\frac{\\pi}{4} D^2}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "P_{load} = \\sigma_P \\times \\frac{\\pi}{4} D^2",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "P_{load} = 0.7 \\times 3.14 \\times \\frac{(300)^2}{4} = 49455 \\text{ N}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\sigma_R = \\frac{P_{load}}{\\frac{\\pi}{4} d^2}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "d^2 = \\frac{P_{load}}{\\frac{\\pi}{4} \\sigma_R}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "d = \\sqrt{\\frac{0.7 \\times \\frac{3.14}{4} \\times (300)^2}{\\frac{3.14}{4} \\times 40}} = \\sqrt{\\frac{0.7 \\times (300)^2}{40}} = 0.1322375 \\times 200 = 00.2020 \\text{ mm (Ans)}",
          "display": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
